data.description: This charming house is a must-see. With its spacious layout it offers both comfort and style! This beautiful home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, New paint and flooring with an ample living area- perfect for gatherings, The kitchen has plenty of counter space for cooking and meal preparation with new stove and Dishwasher that will be installed before close of escrow. The master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet and nice bathroom. The backyard is spacious, nicely landscaped. Located in a desirable neighborhood, this house is close to schools, parks, and shopping. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home.
